                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:55:01.686+09:00">﻿﻿17. The Master said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:36:58.827+09:00">‘You,*</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:37:05.273+09:00"> shall I teach you about understanding something?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:37:12.068+09:00">When you understand something, to recognize that you understand it;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:37:18.519+09:00">but when you do not understand something, to recognize that you do not understand it</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:37:46.247+09:00">—that is understanding.’</seg>
                </p>
